Subject: Re: [VB] '65 trans/clutch slipping?

I have washed my engines with simple green and a pressure washer.  in the compartmentt and below, and had no clutch slipping issues.  This shoudln't get stuff on your clutch.  Even if the engine is really filthoid.

If your clutch is slipping it's probably from an oil leak past the main seal

